mics\nExperience with testing virtual agents supporting customer service\nAttention to details, strong communication skills (especially, communication with stakeholders)\nPermanent Right to Work in Hungary\n\nWHAT YOU'LL GET:\n\n24-month full-time contract with high possibility to extend or switch to permanent. \nExperience in a Global environment.\nAdditional training from our Academy (if required). \nPay transparency - 0-6 months - 7 500 000, 7-12 months - 8 000 000, 13-18 months - 8 500 000, 19-24 months - 9 000 000 HUF/gross/yearly.\nOngoing training and support.\nValuable industry experience. \n\n**This is a hybrid position, working 2-3 days per week from our Client's office in Budapest\nImportant information on Diversity\nWe take great pride in celebrating the diversity of each and every individual who contributes to making Wiley Edge the company it is today and will be in the future. We value diversity both within Wiley Edge and with our partner companies, and we're proud to provide an environment where all our colleagues can flourish. That means promoting a strong culture of equality but, most importantly, inclusion. We never want people to change - only add to the amazing mix of people that work for Wiley Edge.\n \nQuestions about our program and roles? Please get in touch with us at info@wileyedge.com.","departments":[{"id":4007886006,"name":"Technology","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}],"offices":[{"id":4003901006,"name":"Hungary","location":"Hungary","child_ids":[],"parent_id":4003899006}],"compliance":null,"demographic_questions":null,"questions":[{"description":null,"label":"First Name","required":true,"fields":[{"name":"first_name","type":"input_text","values":[]}]},{"description":null,"label":"Last Name","required":true,"fields":[{"name":"last_name","type":"input_text","values":[]}]},{"description":null,"label":"Email","required":true,"fields":[{"name":"email","type":"input_text","values":[]}]},{"description":null,"label":"Phone","required":true,"fie